    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="文档标题"><a href="#文档标题" class="headerlink" title="文档标题"></a>文档标题</h1><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id="三级标题"><a href="#三级标题" class="headerlink" title="三级标题"></a>三级标题</h3><hr><p>[TOC]：目录Table of contents</p><p>[TOC]</p><hr><p><img src=""></p><img src="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/files/attachments/922915342925824/0"><!--通过属性设置图片的宽和高--><img src="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/files/attachments/922915342925824/0" width="300px" height="180"><!--通过样式设置图片的宽和高--><img src="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/files/attachments/922915342925824/0" style="width:300px;height:180px"><!--通过样式设置图片的缩放比例--><img src="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/files/attachments/922915342925824/0" style="zoom:50%"><hr><p><strong>粗体</strong><br><em>斜体</em><br><code>code in line</code><br></p><p>链接：</p><ol><li><p>文字链接：<a href="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/">廖雪峰的官方网站</a></p></li><li><p>自动链接：（只识别www或http://开头的URL地址）（链接为更多emoji）：<br><a href="http://www.webpagefx.com/tools/emoji-cheat-sheet/">http://www.webpagefx.com/tools/emoji-cheat-sheet/</a></p></li><li><p>引用链接：[B站][bilibili]</p><p> [bilibili]: <a href="http://www.bilibili.com/">http://www.bilibili.com/</a></p></li></ol><p><del>删除线</del></p><p>:smile:</p><hr><ol><li>有序列表<ol><li>嵌套</li></ol></li></ol><ul><li><p>无序列表</p><ul><li>嵌套 </li></ul></li><li><p><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox">  任务1</p><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 任务2</li></ul></li></ul><hr><blockquote><p><em>引用</em> [B站][bilibili]</p></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><p><strong>嵌套</strong></p></blockquote></blockquote><hr><table><thead><tr><th align="left">左对齐</th><th align="center">居中</th><th align="right">右对齐</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><strong>1</strong></td><td align="center">[B站][bilibili]</td><td align="right"><a href="http://www.bilibili.com/">www.bilibili.com</a></td></tr><tr><td align="left"><em>2</em></td><td align="center">[B站][bilibili]</td><td align="right"><a href="http://www.bilibili.com/">www.bilibili.com</a></td></tr></tbody></table><hr><p>代码块</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(c)    <span class="comment"># 代码块。或以TAB或4个空格开头</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><u>下画线</u></p><hr><p>内联系数学公式</p><p>$ f(x, y) = \frac{x^2}{y^3} $</p><p>$ f(x, y) = \sqrt[n]{x^2}{y^3} $</p><p>$ f(x_1, x_2, \ldots, x_n) = x_1 + x_2 + \cdots + x_n $<br>$$<br>\mathbf{V}_1 \times \mathbf{V}_2 = \begin{vmatrix}<br>\mathbf{i} &amp; \mathbf{j} &amp; \mathbf{k} \<br>\frac{\partial X}{\partial u} &amp; \frac{\partial Y}{\partial u} &amp; 0 \<br>\frac{\partial X}{\partial v} &amp; \frac{\partial Y}{\partial v} &amp; 0 \<br>\end{vmatrix}<br>$$</p><hr><p>下标：H<del>2</del>O</p><p>上标：X^2^+Y^2^</p><hr><p>==高亮==</p><hr><!--注释--><p>清除样式：Ctrl+\</p><hr><p>角注<a href="%E5%AF%B9%E8%A7%92%E6%B3%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0">^参考</a></p><hr><p>图表</p><ol><li><p>序列图</p><p> <code>js-sequence-diagrams语法</code>，参考<a href="http://bramp.github.io/js-sequence-diagrams/%E3%80%82">http://bramp.github.io/js-sequence-diagrams/。</a></p></li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">张三 -&gt; 李四:李四，吃了吗？</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Note right of 李四:我显示在李四的右边</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">李四 --&gt; 张三:好久不见，三儿，我刚吃过！</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li><p>流程图</p><p> <code>flowchart.js语法</code>，参考<a href="http://flowchart.js.org/%E3%80%82">http://flowchart.js.org/。</a></p> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">st=&gt;start: 开始</span><br><span class="line">op=&gt;operation: 我是帅哥</span><br><span class="line">cond=&gt;condition: Yes or No?</span><br><span class="line">e=&gt;end: 结束</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op-&gt;cond</span><br><span class="line">cond(yes)-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">cond(no)-&gt;op</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>Mermaid</p><ul><li><p><code>Mermaid序列图语法</code>，参考<a href="https://knsc.github.io/mermaid/#loops32">https://knsc.github.io/mermaid/#loops32</a></p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%% 序列图举例（我是注释）</span><br><span class="line">sequenceDiagram</span><br><span class="line">张三-&gt;&gt;李四: 李四：吃了吗？</span><br><span class="line">李四--&gt;&gt;张三: 好久不见，三儿，我刚吃过！</span><br><span class="line">Note right of 李四: 我显示在李四的右边</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>Mermaid流程图语法</code>，参考<a href="https://knsv.github.io/mermaid/#graph18">https://knsv.github.io/mermaid/#graph18</a></p></li></ul> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph TD</span><br><span class="line">A[开始] --&gt;B(我是帅哥)</span><br><span class="line">B --&gt; C&#123;Yes or No?&#125;</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt;|Yes| D[结束]</span><br><span class="line">C --&gt;|No| B</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>Mermaid甘特图语法</code>，参考<a href="https://knsv.github.io/mermaid/index.html#mermaid-cli">https://knsv.github.io/mermaid/index.html#mermaid-cli</a></li></ul> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%% 甘特图示例</span><br><span class="line">gantt</span><br><span class="line">dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD</span><br><span class="line">title 项目开发周期</span><br><span class="line">section 需求评审</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">需求评审:2018-01-01,2018-01-02</span><br><span class="line">section 功能开发</span><br><span class="line">开发编码:2018-01-03,2018-01-08</span><br><span class="line">开发自测:2018-01-08,2018-01-09</span><br><span class="line">section 项目测试</span><br><span class="line">第1轮测试:2018-01-09,2018-01-14</span><br><span class="line">第2轮测试:2018-01-14,2018-01-16</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><p>使用HTML标签</p><ol><li><p>文件颜色和大小</p><p> <span style="color:green"> 绿色 </span><span style="color:#fa0;font-size:20px"> 黄色 </span><span style="color:red;font-size:30px"> 红色 </span></p></li><li><p>嵌入网页</p> <iframe height='265' scrolling='yes' title='B站' src='https://www.bilibili.com' frameborder='no' allowtransparency='true' allowfullscreen='true' style='width: 100%;'></iframe></li><li><p>插入视频</p> <video src="./imgs/video.mov" /></li></ol><hr><p>转义:不被渲染。<br>\特殊符号</p><ul><li>\  </li><li>*  </li><li>`  </li><li>_  </li><li>{}  </li><li>[]  </li></ul><hr><hr><hr><ul><li><a href="#%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%981">1</a></li><li><a href="#%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%9811">扩展语法</a></li></ul><hr><p>排版技巧</p><ol><li><p>关于空格<br><br> 加空格：</p><pre><code> 1. 英文标点（,.:;?）&lt;br&gt;Example: Visit an Apple Store, call 1-800-MY-APPLE.&lt;br&gt; 2. 使用&gt;（半角）标识路径&lt;br&gt;Series A &gt; B &gt; C.&lt;br&gt;</code></pre><p> 不加空格：</p><ol><li>中文标点<br>MACBOOK Pro（15英寸，2016年年末）</li><li>数字和百分号之间<br>最高提升103%之多</li><li>数字和单位符号之间<br>最高达 3.1GB/s，15英寸机型首次提供2TB容量</li><li>英文和数字组合成的名字之间<br>双核 Inter Core I7 处理器</li><li>/（半角）表示“或”、“路径”<br>/study/learn-markdown.md</li><li>货币符号后<br>$149</li><li>负号后<br>3 - 5 = -2</li></ol></li><li><p>全角和半角</p><ul><li>全角：中文标点符号 ， 。 ； ： ！ #</li><li>半角：英文标点符号 ,  .  ;  :  !  #</li></ul></li><li><p>正确的英文大小写<br> iPhone7、MacOS、iPad Pro 等</p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
